esqlQuery.esql:
// Alert triggers when the notificationsfailed exceeds the recommended threshold value {0} within the look back time window.
// The alert is grouped by cloud account id, cloud region and topic name.
// You can adjust the threshold value by modifying the notificationsfailed in the WHERE clause.
FROM metrics-aws.sns-default
| STATS notificationsfailed=avg(aws.sns.NumberOfNotificationsFailed.sum) by cloud.account.id, cloud.region, aws.dimensions.TopicName
| WHERE notificationsfailed > 0
